{"type": "article", "id": 25243, "title": "可做边桌或凳子的小家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-11T06:59:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607140957Rpx012fuLO4v8bkc.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个方形的小家具即可以做边桌也可以做凳子，日本设计团队 The Twig Co.从树中获得灵感，将支撑结构设计成树干的形式，有一个较粗的主干和两个细分支连接座位和地面，构成了一种平衡。设计团队认为树连接了天堂和地面，而它的自然特征也带来了一种温和的居家气氛。售价 175 美元，<a href=\"http://twigcreative.myshopify.com/products/kyoto\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140955OIvTBsJ6nAM1rbCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140956JTqbgfUGt9iNXRms.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140956ep1ABbJ4Sd2zR7Gw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140957YCpwsaVEiv8AgUdx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607140957dubTjBUfDsM82KAi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}